{"data": [{"id": "4743315", "title": "German Bunds Still Face Pressure Relative To Risk-Free Rates", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"German flag fluttering front of Reichstag building. Berlin, Germany\" data-id=\"1196974543\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5864px\" height=\"3909px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">arsenisspyros</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/benjamin-schroeder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Benjamin Schroeder</a></em></p> <h2>The Bund spread remains under pressure, but we also see arguments for stabilisation</h2> <p>There had been a general sense that the central banks' quantitative tightening paired with ongoing high funding needs would require a reassessment of sovereign</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743315-german-bunds-face-pressure-relative-to-risk-free-rates", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:00:00"}, {"id": "4743301", "title": "XLK: Addressing The Unappealing Aspects", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Artificial intelligence circuit board 1\" data-id=\"1370479405\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1032px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Kitchen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Technology Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XLK\" title=\"The Technology Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF\">XLK</a></span>) is the go-to fund for concentrated technology exposure. However, many find the concentration in its top three stocks unappealing, and XLK's simple methodology can lead to underperformance when individual industry groups are</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743301-xlk-etf-addressing-unappealing-aspects", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:48:09"}, {"id": "4743298", "title": "Magnolia Oil & Gas: Continued Improvements In Capital Efficiency", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil pumps and wind mill during sunset.\" data-id=\"2151247502\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"947px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Torsten Asmus</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Magnolia Oil &amp; Gas Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MGY\" title=\"Magnolia Oil &amp; Gas Corporation\">MGY</a></span>) <a href=\"https://www.magnoliaoilgas.com/investors/press-releases/year/2024/10-30-2024-200204462\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.magnoliaoilgas.com/investors/press-releases/year/2024/10-30-2024-200204462\" target=\"_blank\">reported Q3 2024 production</a> that was in line with expectations, despite some temporary third-party midstream issues that mainly affected its natural gas and NGL production.</p> <p>Magnolia's oil production has been tracking slightly ahead of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743298-magnolia-oil-and-gas-continued-improvements-in-capital-efficiency", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:40:14"}, {"id": "4743295", "title": "DRDGOLD: Profitability Is Improving. An Attractive Dip May Not Be Far Off (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold Ingot\" data-id=\"184092819\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">t_kimura</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>A \u201cBuy\u201d Rating for Shares of DRDGOLD Limited</h2> <p>This analysis gives DRDGOLD Limited (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DRD\" title=\"DRDGOLD Limited\">DRD</a></span>) a Buy rating, reflecting an upgrade from the Hold rating given in the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4703732-drdgold-has-steam-but-better-from-a-dip-drd-stock\">previous analysis</a>.</p> <p>DRDGOLD Limited, hereinafter referred to as \"DRDGOLD\", headquartered in Johannesburg, South Africa, is a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743295-drdgold-profitability-is-improving-an-attractive-dip-may-not-be-far-off-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:34:30"}, {"id": "4743322", "title": "Gold Eyes $2,700 As Fed Rate Cut Looms, Geopolitics In Focus", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold coins with hundred dollar bills\" data-id=\"142096634\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1331px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Anthony Bradshaw</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <p>Gold has started the week on the offensive as the stars have somewhat realigned for the precious metal. The regime change and geopolitical developments in Syria, coupled with a Chinese monetary policy shift and a weaker</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743322-gold-eyes-2700-fed-rate-cut-looms-geopolitics-in-focus", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:32:00"}, {"id": "4743290", "title": "Which Is Better For Christmas Cheer: Diageo Or Pernod Ricard?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pouring whiskey from bottle into glass on wooden barrel against black background, closeup\" data-id=\"1506161553\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Liudmila Chernetska</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Consumer Discretionary stocks have been in the doldrums over the last few years. As interest rates have been on the rise, consumers have generally been tightening their belts, and directing their purchases towards more essential items.</p> <p>As a result, revenues have</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1506161553/image_1506161553.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743290-which-is-better-for-christmas-cheer-diageo-or-pernod-ricard", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:23:31"}, {"id": "4743289", "title": "MongoDB: On Firmer Footing As Consumption Drives Re-Acceleration (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"MongoDB office in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1157051255\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Michael Vi</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>While the majority of the tech sector has seen blockbuster gains this year, one major category of holdouts has been infrastructure-related software companies that price their products based on usage. This year, as IT chiefs pulled back on spending amid a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1157051255/image_1157051255.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743289-mongodb-stock-firmer-footing-consumption-drives-re-acceleration-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:20:58"}, {"id": "4743287", "title": "Qualitative And Contrarian Outlook For 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Laughing couple with arms raised riding roller coaster at amusement park\" data-id=\"1083856232\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The market has had a good year in 2024, with the S&amp;P500 (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500\u00ae ETF Trust\">SPY</a></span>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" class=\"ticker-link\">SP500</a>) up +26.9% year to date, driven by technology stocks and the AI revolution. Some people say bubble, others say this time is different. Maybe, maybe</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1083856232/image_1083856232.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743287-qualitative-and-contrarian-outlook-for-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:13:51"}, {"id": "4743303", "title": "Eurozone Bond Spreads: A Reordering In Progress", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"European flag in Frankfurt, Germany.\" data-id=\"1455668014\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1157px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">littleclie</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/benjamin-schroeder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Benjamin Schroeder</a></em></p> <h2>Spread risks look more contained and idiosyncratic</h2> <p>The market seems to sense that eurozone risks are by now largely contained, and we are looking more at idiosyncratic country stories. The reaction of Bund swap spreads to episodes</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455668014/image_1455668014.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743303-eurozone-bond-spreads-reordering-progress", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:00:00"}, {"id": "4743302", "title": "ceo-john-stankey-at-ubs-global-media-and-communications-conference", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by AT&amp;T Inc. in conjunction with this event.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106097\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743302-ceo-john-stankey-ubs-global-media-and-communications-conference", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:51:10"}]}